summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2006 TRAIL MANOR TRAVEL TRAILER, MODEL NUMBER 2720(NA). THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE EXTERIOR LIGHTING WIRING WAS DEFECTIVE AND WOULD CAUSE THE LIGHTS TO FAIL INTERMITTENTLY. THE CONTACT STATED THAT WIRING CONNECTORS WERE NOT CRIMPED CORRECTLY AND EXPELLING FROM THE CONNECTIONS. NEITHER THE DEALER NOR MANUFACTURER WAS NOTIFIED OF THE FAILURE. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT REPAIRED. THE VIN WAS UNAVAILABLE.  THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 14,000.
